    "We started our analyses by calculating the absolute numbers of HCRs and their shares among all authors.",
    "We found that the absolute numbers and shares significantly differ between the five variants.",
    "Variant-0 (Clarivate) led to the smallest set of HCRs with n = 14,349 and a share of 0.09% of all authors in the period from 2010 to 2018.",
    "Variant-1 resulted in the largest list of HCRs in absolute and relative terms (318,913 and 2%).",
